data.description: This 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom ranch style home offers plenty of space for families or for entertaining guests. New plumbing was installed throughout the home in February 2023. The fenced in back yard has plenty of space and would be perfect for pets or cookouts with friends and family. This property has a great location that is within walking distance of plenty of dining and entertainment options. Easy access to both U.S. 31 and I-65.
